  "body": "See question here: https://github.com/libp2p/go-libp2p/issues/548\r\n\r\nThe problem is that host.Peerstore().Peers() returns a list of all peers that have ever connected to the node. Not just the ones that are currently connected. As such, our peer count metric always increases but never decreases. \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/9999b3280aa3a7296a2646c2c0543971a17ff39a/shared/p2p/monitoring.go#L39-L42",
